30:35.660 --> 30:36.854
WHAT WOULD YOU DO?

30:36.900 --> 30:40.893
- LOOK, SANDRA...

30:40.940 --> 30:42.669
- DON'T FILL HER HEAD
WITH FALSE HOPES.

30:42.700 --> 30:44.634
SHE'S LOOKING AT LIFE.
TAKE THE PLEA.

30:44.670 --> 30:46.262
- LIFE?
- DO NOT TAKE THE PLEA!

30:46.310 --> 30:47.538
HORNSTOCK,
GET BACK IN THERE.

30:47.570 --> 30:48.776
BUY US ANOTHER HOUR
WITH THE JUDGE.

30:48.810 --> 30:51.472
PLEASE.

30:51.510 --> 30:53.842
SANDRA, DON'T WORRY, OKAY?
I'M GONNA FIND SOMETHING.

30:53.880 --> 30:55.370
SOMEWHERE.

30:55.420 --> 30:58.412
YOU HAVE
MY HAND-TO-HEAD PROMISE.

31:04.260 --> 31:06.182
I GOT NOTHING.

31:06.230 --> 31:07.686
- THE ONLY PROBLEM
IS HORNSTOCK

31:07.730 --> 31:09.425
IS DUE BACK IN COURT
ANY MINUTE NOW.

31:09.460 --> 31:10.597
- THERE'S GOTTA BE
A HIDDEN CLUE SOMEWHERE.

31:10.630 --> 31:12.063
GO DOWN THERE AND STALL!

31:12.100 --> 31:13.169
- I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO DO THAT, SHAWN.

31:13.200 --> 31:14.690
- YOU ARE MATTHEW MCCONAUGHEY,

31:14.740 --> 31:16.492
AND THIS IS YOUR TIME TO KILL.
NOW, GO!

31:16.540 --> 31:17.962
- MAN!

31:18.010 --> 31:21.173
- KEEP YOUR SHIRT ON THOUGH.

31:21.210 --> 31:23.030
COME ON.

31:23.080 --> 31:26.004
- MY PATIENCE
IS RUNNING THINNER, COUNSELOR.

31:26.050 --> 31:28.314
IF YOUR CONSULTANTS
DON'T SHOW UP HERE SOON,

31:28.350 --> 31:30.568
I'M GOING TO SEND THIS JURY OFF
FOR DELIBERATIONS.

31:30.620 --> 31:32.679
- NO, NO, NO.
NO, SIR, I--

31:32.720 --> 31:35.052
I REALLY DON'T--
- WHY ARE YOU FIDGETING?

31:35.090 --> 31:37.308
- OH, I DID HAVE, UM, A LITTLE
ISSUE DURING THE BREAK, SIR,

31:37.360 --> 31:39.089
BUT I CLEARED IT UP
WITH A MYLANTA.

31:39.130 --> 31:40.950
- YOUR HONOR,
THE STATE IS STILL WILLING

31:41.000 --> 31:42.422
TO ACCEPT THE PLEA.

31:42.460 --> 31:43.961
OBVIOUSLY COUNSEL
IS CRUMBLING.

31:44.000 --> 31:45.763
AND FRANKLY,
IT'S HARD TO WATCH.

31:45.800 --> 31:48.394
- AH, WELL,
HERE COMES ONE OF THEM.

31:48.440 --> 31:49.634
- HOW'D SHAWN DO?
- NOTHING.

31:49.670 --> 31:50.830
HE'S STILL ON IT.
- WHAT? NO!

31:50.870 --> 31:52.906
NO, IT'S TOO LATE!

31:52.940 --> 31:55.374
I DON'T HAVE ANY WITNESSES.
I DON'T HAVE ANY MOTIONS.

31:55.410 --> 31:58.470
SANDRA...
I'M SORRY.

32:11.990 --> 32:13.480
- I GOT IT.

32:13.530 --> 32:16.351
[phone vibrates]

32:18.200 --> 32:20.566
- YOUR HONOR,
AT THIS JUNCTURE, I--

32:20.600 --> 32:22.898
- NOT JUST YET, YOUR HONOR.

32:22.940 --> 32:25.135
IF I MAY,
I'D LIKE TO ADDRESS THE COURT.

32:25.170 --> 32:28.571
- OBJECTION. THIS MAN
CANNOT ADDRESS ANY COURT.

32:28.610 --> 32:30.168
- YOUNG MAN, HAVE YOU EVER
ATTENDED A LAW SCHOOL?

32:30.210 --> 32:32.075
- JUST MS. FINKELMAN'S
SIXTH-GRADE CLASS, SIR,

32:32.110 --> 32:34.010
"ME, YOU, AND THE LAW."

32:34.050 --> 32:35.972
- WELL,
IT IS UNDER MY DISCRETION

32:36.020 --> 32:38.909
TO ALLOW ANY TESTIMONY
THAT MAY SPEAK TO THE TRUTH

32:38.950 --> 32:42.056
IN THIS CASE--
TINY LEASH. GO.

32:42.090 --> 32:45.389
- OH, UH--
[clears throat]

32:45.430 --> 32:46.749
THANK YOU, SIR.

32:46.790 --> 32:48.929
UH, EXCUSE ME.
[clears throat]

32:48.960 --> 32:50.791
EXCUSE ME.

32:50.830 --> 32:51.865
EXCUSE ME.
[clears throat]

32:51.900 --> 32:53.367
EXCUSE ME.

32:53.400 --> 32:54.628
I WOULD LIKE TO, UH,
JUST, UH---

32:54.670 --> 32:56.638
- JUST WHAT?
SPEAK!

32:56.670 --> 32:59.639
- EXCUSE ME, SIR,
BUT YOU ARE BEING RUDE.

32:59.670 --> 33:01.001
IS IT BECAUSE I'M A YUTE?

33:01.040 --> 33:02.837
- A WHAT?
- WHAT'S A YUTE?

33:02.880 --> 33:05.405
- OH, A YUTE, A YUTE.
IT'S A YOUTH.

33:05.450 --> 33:07.247
IT'S FROM MY COUSIN VINNY.
TERRIFIC FILM, SIR.

33:07.280 --> 33:10.078
- OBJECTION, YOUR HONOR.
IT'S OKAY, DECENT AT BEST.

33:10.120 --> 33:11.917
- I DON'T CARE WHAT COUSIN
IT'S COMING FROM.

33:11.950 --> 33:13.679
I'M ABOUT TO HOLD YOU TWO
IN CONTEMPT.

33:13.720 --> 33:16.450
- SO THE PLEA BARGAIN
IS JUST OUT?

33:16.490 --> 33:17.787
[phone vibrates]
WE CAN'T GO BACK NOW

33:17.820 --> 33:19.378
AND GET THE--

33:19.430 --> 33:20.522
DO SOMETHING.

33:20.560 --> 33:24.997
- UH...

33:25.030 --> 33:28.158
TH EY--THEY--
THEY BEAT UP ON A WEAKLING.

33:28.200 --> 33:31.465
THE REST IS JUST SMOKE-FILLED,
COFFEEHOUSE CRAP!

33:31.510 --> 33:34.570
THEY TORTURED AND TORMENTED
A WEAKER KID, AND WHY?

33:34.610 --> 33:36.475
BECAUSE HE COULDN'T RUN
VERY FAST.

33:36.510 --> 33:37.602
- A FEW GOOD MEN!
- EXACTLY.

33:37.640 --> 33:39.107
- I'M WARNING YOU.

33:39.150 --> 33:40.708
- YOU THINK YOU HAVE A MONOPOLY
ON THE TRUTH?

33:40.750 --> 33:42.741
- ALL RIGHT, THAT'S IT.
YOU ARE IN CONTEMPT.

33:44.350 --> 33:46.386
YOU NEED ME ON THAT WALL.

33:46.420 --> 33:48.012
[gavelbangs]
-ENOUGH!

33:48.060 --> 33:51.826
BAILIFF, PLEASE REMAND
THIS YUTE INTO CUSTODY.

33:51.860 --> 33:53.521
- COME ON, SON.

33:53.560 --> 33:55.198
- DON'T YOU
"COME ON, SON" ME.

33:55.230 --> 33:58.688
I AM A LAWYER AND AN OFFICER
IN THE UNITED STATES NAW.

33:58.730 --> 34:01.164
AND YOU, SIR,
ARE UNDER ARREST,

34:01.200 --> 34:03.395
YOU SON OF A BITCH.

34:03.440 --> 34:04.532
- HEY.

34:04.570 --> 34:06.208
DO BONFIRE.

34:06.240 --> 34:07.764
- WHAT DOES IT MATTER
THE COLOR OF A MAN'S SKIN

34:07.810 --> 34:09.971
IF MEN OF THE CLOTH,
MEN OF GOD

34:10.010 --> 34:11.773
TAKE THE PRIME CUTS?

34:11.810 --> 34:12.970
- I LIKED THAT ONE.
- ME TOO.

34:13.010 --> 34:14.819
I HOPE THEY DON'T REMAKE IT.

34:14.850 --> 34:17.045
DR. TOWLER TOLD ME
TO CHANGE THE FORM.

34:17.080 --> 34:19.583
HE TOLD ME TO CHANGE THE "1"
TO A "9."

34:19.620 --> 34:22.851
HE SAID I'D NEVER WORK AGAIN.
WHO WERE THESE MEN?

34:22.890 --> 34:24.323
WHO WERE THESE MEN?

34:24.360 --> 34:25.952
I WANTED TO BE A NURSE!

34:25.990 --> 34:29.153
[fake crying]

34:29.200 --> 34:31.464
- YO, WHAT WAS THAT LAST ONE?

34:31.500 --> 34:33.092
- THE VERDICT.
PAUL NEWMAN.

34:33.130 --> 34:35.030
- NEVER SAW IT, BUT I LIKE
THAT DUDE'S POPCORN.

34:35.070 --> 34:36.992
- SHAWN, I DID IT!
I DID IT!

34:37.040 --> 34:39.964
- GOOD JOB, BUDDY.
I'LL TAKE IT FROM HERE.

34:40.010 --> 34:41.637
- [struggling]

34:44.150 --> 34:45.799
- MISS ME?

34:45.850 --> 34:46.976
HEY, JULES.

34:47.010 --> 34:48.944
- [sneezes]
- BLESS YOU.

34:48.980 --> 34:50.709
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN
OF THE COURT,

34:50.750 --> 34:54.652
JUROR NUMBER FIVE,
AND THE HONORABLE JUDGE H. LEES,

34:54.690 --> 34:56.555
THE DEFENSE WOULD LIKE TO CALL
TO THE STAND

34:56.590 --> 34:58.649
MR. MORTIMER CAMP.

34:58.690 --> 34:59.987
- OBJECTION!

35:00.030 --> 35:01.395
MR. CAMP IS NOT ON TRIAL HERE,

35:01.430 --> 35:04.024
AND A PSYCHIC
CANNOT SPEAK TO WITNESSES.

35:04.060 --> 35:05.721
- JUDGE, I NOW HAVE EVIDENCE

35:05.770 --> 35:07.089
THAT WILL SHINE A SHOCKING

35:07.130 --> 35:10.566
AND VIBRANT LIGHT
ON THIS CASE.

35:10.600 --> 35:12.636
- YOUR HONOR,
AI-TER WHAT WE JUST SAW,

35:12.670 --> 35:14.206
YOU COULDN'T POSSIBLY
ALLOW THIS.

35:14.240 --> 35:17.505
- YOUR HONOR!

35:20.310 --> 35:22.949
MR. CAMP,
YOUR WIFE WANTED A DIVORCE.

35:22.980 --> 35:24.789
YOU DID NOT.
TRUE?

35:24.820 --> 35:27.345
- SHE WAS UNHAPPY.
I UNDERSTOOD.

35:27.390 --> 35:29.187
- SOMETIMES THINGS
ARE A LOT MORE ONE-SIDED

35:29.220 --> 35:31.825
THAN WE WOULD LIKE THEM TO BE,
AREN'T THEY, MR. CAMP?

35:31.860 --> 35:36.422
FOR EXAMPLE, I CAN RELATE
BECAUSE I'M A PSYCHIC.

35:36.460 --> 35:38.928
WHICH MEANS LOVE
IS EVEN MORE DIFFICULT FOR ME

35:38.970 --> 35:40.722
THAN IT IS FOR YOU.

35:40.770 --> 35:44.092
BUT THERE IS A WOMAN
IN THIS COURTROOM RIGHT NOW,

35:44.140 --> 35:46.108
A LITTLE SLICE
OF BLONDE PERFECTION,

35:46.140 --> 35:48.131
A PERFECT LY FORMED BEIGNET

35:48.180 --> 35:50.774
LIGHTLY DUSTED
WITH POWDERED SUGAR

35:50.810 --> 35:52.675
AND A BADGE.

35:52.710 --> 35:54.211
THE FIRST TIME
THAT I SAW HER,

35:54.250 --> 35:56.741
I HAD A VISION
THAT WE WOULD BE MARRIED,

35:56.780 --> 36:00.318
AND WE WOULD HAVE
SO MANY KIDS

36:00.350 --> 36:02.250
THAT MOST OF THEM WOULD HAVE
TO BE PUT UP FOR ADOPTION.

36:02.290 --> 36:05.657
- WHERE ARE YOU GOING
WITH THIS, MR. SPENCER?

36:05.690 --> 36:07.021
- JUDGE, I CAN'T ANSWER
THAT QUESTION FOR YOU.

36:07.060 --> 36:08.322
I MEAN, WE WORK TOGETHER.

36:08.360 --> 36:10.191
IT'D BE LIKE THE TWO OF YOU

36:10.230 --> 36:12.266
HAVING A CONNECTION
AND WONDERING IF IT'S REAL OR...

36:12.300 --> 36:14.165
- [sighs]
- IS IT REAL, HOW DO YOU KNOW?

36:14.200 --> 36:17.658
YOU DON'T.

36:17.700 --> 36:20.533
MR. CAMP, YOU COULDN'T
MAKE YOUR WIFE LOVE YOU,

36:20.570 --> 36:22.879
SO THAT MADE YOU
EVEN MORE JEALOUS, DIDN'T IT?

36:22.910 --> 36:24.377
- NO MORE JEALOUS
THAN ANY OTHER MAN WOULD BE

36:24.410 --> 36:25.707
IN THE SAME POSITION.

36:25.750 --> 36:28.048
- SHE WAS LYING TO YOU!

36:28.080 --> 36:31.345
SHE TOLD YOU SHE WAS TAKING
TENNIS LESSONS Al-TER WORK.

36:31.390 --> 36:33.688
DID YOU REALLY BELIEVE THAT?

36:33.720 --> 36:35.358
- OF COURSE I DID.
SHE'S MY WIFE.

36:35.390 --> 36:37.255
I MEAN, LOOK, I KNOW I'M
A REALLY GOOD-LOOKING NEWSCASTER

36:37.290 --> 36:39.554
AND I COULD AARON ECKHART
MY WAY AROUND TOWN IF I--

36:39.590 --> 36:41.228
- NO, NO, NOT AARON ECKHART.

36:41.260 --> 36:43.797
- I COULD PATRICK WILSON
MY WAY AROUND TOWN.

36:43.830 --> 36:45.263
- BETTER.

36:45.300 --> 36:48.292
- YOU WERE DECEIVED!

36:48.340 --> 36:50.558
HERE'S THE IRONY--
SHE WAS ACTUALLY

36:50.600 --> 36:52.500
GOING TO SEE
A MARRIAGE THERAPIST INSTEAD.

36:52.540 --> 36:55.429
- YOUR TENNIS LESSON'S
BEEN CHANGED TO 5:00 P.M. TODAY.

36:55.480 --> 36:59.769
- SHE WAS SEEING DR. ROSEN,
THE MARRIAGE THERAPIST, INSTEAD,

36:59.810 --> 37:01.209
AND IF SHE'D
ONLY TOLD YOU THAT,

37:01.250 --> 37:03.115
PERHAPS YOU WOULDN'T HAVE
TAKEN MATTERS

37:03.150 --> 37:05.983
INTO YOUR OWN HANDS.

37:06.020 --> 37:08.147
- YOU WERE CONVINCED THAT SHE
WAS CHEATING ON YOU WITH HALE,

37:08.190 --> 37:10.511
SO YOU DECIDED TO CATCH THEM
IN THE ACT.

37:17.230 --> 37:19.198
ON THE SET...

37:19.230 --> 37:22.734
'CAUSE YOU KNEW JACKSON
LIKED TO TAKE HIS LADIES THERE

37:22.770 --> 37:26.866
TO SEDUCE THEM,
TO...

37:26.910 --> 37:28.468
FILM HIS TRYSTS.

37:28.510 --> 37:31.138
- I GUESS SOME GIRLS
ARE TURNED ON BY A WEATHER SET.

37:31.180 --> 37:33.102
- YOU HEARD JACKSON ENTER
THAT NIGHT.

37:33.150 --> 37:35.015
IT WAS DARK, SHADOWY.

37:35.050 --> 37:37.371
YOU PREMEDITATED THIS MURDER,

37:37.420 --> 37:39.718
BUT YOU WERE CONVINCED
IT WAS YOUR WIFE.

37:39.750 --> 37:41.854
AND YOU KNEW HE'D BRING HER BACK
TO THE STUDIO

37:41.890 --> 37:43.755
WHERE HE SECRETLY FILMS
HIS TRYSTS.

37:43.790 --> 37:46.054
USING THE TECHNICIAN'S
GREEN SCREEN SUIT,

37:46.090 --> 37:47.751
YOU KNEW
YOU'D REMAIN UNDETECTED.

37:47.790 --> 37:50.020
YOU WAITED FOR THEM
TO DROP OUT OF FRAME--

37:50.060 --> 37:51.925
- AND YOU KNOCKED
THAT POOR GIRL OUT COLD

37:51.970 --> 37:53.824
AND STABBED YOU
SOME JACKSON HALE.

37:53.870 --> 37:56.236
- THEN YOU NOTICED
IT WASN'T CONNIE AT ALL,

37:56.270 --> 37:58.135
IT WAS MY CLIENT
SANDRA PANITCH,

37:58.170 --> 38:00.331
AN INNOCENT GIRL WHO WALKED
INTO A DEADLY LOVE TRIANGLE.

38:00.370 --> 38:02.770
- I DID, I DID.
I WALKED RIGHT INTO IT.

38:02.810 --> 38:04.277
BUT I HAD ONE DRINK,

38:04.310 --> 38:05.948
AND YOU KNOW,
MY FRIENDS WERE TEASING ME

38:05.980 --> 38:07.447
BECAUSE I NEVER HAD
A ONE-NIGHT STAND.

38:07.480 --> 38:08.970
SO I THOUGHT, LIKE,
OH, TONIGHT'S THE NIGHT.

38:09.020 --> 38:10.749
MAYBE I SHOULD DO IT.
- SANDY, SHH, SHH.

38:10.780 --> 38:14.147
- AND HIS TEETH WERE SO WHITE,
AND HIS HAIR WAS SHIN--

38:14.190 --> 38:16.249
- SINCE JACKSON HALE
WAS NOT SLEEPING WITH YOUR WIFE,

38:16.290 --> 38:18.451
YOU THOUGHT YOU COULD STILL
PUT YOUR MARRIAGE BACK TOGETHER.

38:18.490 --> 38:20.481
- AND YOU TRIED
TO PIN IT ON SANDRA PANITCH.

38:20.530 --> 38:23.522
- AND YOU THOUGHT YOU COULD GET
AWAY WITH FIRST-DEGREE MURDER.

38:23.560 --> 38:26.028
- THAT IS
A COMPELLING COURTROOM DRAMA

38:26.070 --> 38:28.595
YOU'VE WRITTEN THERE.
GOOD LUCK PROVING IT.

38:28.640 --> 38:30.733
- OH, WE'RE ABOUT To PROVE IT...
[glggleSJ

38:30.770 --> 38:33.739
RIGHT NOW.

38:33.770 --> 38:36.000
OFFICER,
THE MONITOR, PLEASE.

38:38.240 --> 38:40.447
I PRESENT--

38:40.480 --> 38:42.209
- SO THIS IS
WHERE THE NEWS HAPPENS?

38:42.250 --> 38:43.945
- OH, FORGET ABOUT THE NEWS.

38:43.980 --> 38:45.117
THIS IS ALL ABOUT THE WEATHER.

38:45.150 --> 38:47.118
- THIS PROVES NOTHING.

38:47.150 --> 38:50.017
I'M NOT THERE.
[laughing] I'M NOT THERE.

38:50.060 --> 38:52.187
- MR. SPENCER,
I SEE NO EVIDENCE OF MR. CAMP

38:52.230 --> 38:53.481
IN THIS VIDEO AT ALL.

38:53.530 --> 38:55.191
- PRECISELY, JUDGE.

38:55.230 --> 38:58.097
YOU SEE, MR. CAMP WORE
A GREEN SUIT THAT NIGHT.

38:58.130 --> 39:00.018
HE KNEW WE WOULDN'T BE ABLE
TO SEE HIM ON THIS TAPE,

39:00.070 --> 39:01.992
BECAUSE HE KNEW
HIS GREEN SUIT

39:02.040 --> 39:05.862
WOULD NOT BE VISIBLE IN FRONT
OF THE GREEN SCREEN BACKGROUND.

39:05.910 --> 39:07.662
BUT HIS PINKIE WOULD.

39:07.710 --> 39:09.200
- WHAT IS HE EVEN
TALKING ABOUT?

39:09.240 --> 39:10.468
- LOOK, THERE YOU ARE,
STANDING UP,

39:10.510 --> 39:12.307
STILL INVISIBLE
AFTER THE DIRTY DEED.

39:12.350 --> 39:14.944
BUT THERE'S ONE THING
YOU DIDN'T KNOW.

39:14.980 --> 39:17.175
ALL OF YOUR DIRTY STABBING

39:17.220 --> 39:18.983
CAUSED YOU TO TEAR
ONE OF THE FINGERS

39:19.020 --> 39:21.284
OF YOUR GREEN-SUITED GLOVE.

39:21.320 --> 39:23.413
THAT...

39:23.460 --> 39:26.827
IS YOUR PINKIE STICKING OUT
FROM BEHIND THAT LARGE BUILDING.

39:26.860 --> 39:28.179
- OBJECTION!

39:28.230 --> 39:29.424
HOW WOULD THE DEFENSE
POSSIBLY PROVE

39:29.460 --> 39:31.519
THAT IT'S MR. CAMP'S PINKIE?

39:31.570 --> 39:33.959
- I FOUND MYSELF
WONDERING THAT VERY SAME THING

39:34.000 --> 39:38.130
AS I STARED OUT INTO
THE TWINKLING SANTA BARBARA SKY.

39:38.170 --> 39:42.334
BUT THEN I REALIZED ONE
OF THOSE TWINKLES ISN'T A STAR.

39:42.380 --> 39:44.473
I KNOW WHAT TORE THAT SUIT.

39:44.510 --> 39:48.002
IT'S AN OPAL STONE
FROM A PINKIE RING.

39:48.050 --> 39:50.644
BUT NOT JUST
ANY PINKIE RING...

39:50.680 --> 39:51.942
- AH!
- SORRY.

39:51.990 --> 39:54.185
THAT'S WHAT I GET
FOR NOT LOOKING.

39:54.220 --> 39:55.414
- WHAT ARE YOU--

39:55.460 --> 39:57.985
- THAT...
PINKIE RING.

39:58.020 --> 40:02.593
[crowd murmuring]

40:02.630 --> 40:07.363
GAME, SET, MATCH.

40:07.400 --> 40:11.131
ANY FINAL WORDS,
MR. CAMP?

40:12.340 --> 40:14.069
- [scoffs]

40:15.510 --> 40:17.068
I LOVE YOU, CONNIE.

40:17.110 --> 40:18.998
I JUST WANTED US
TO BE HAPPY TOGETHER.

40:19.050 --> 40:21.439
I WOULD'VE DONE
ANYTHING FOR YOU.

40:21.480 --> 40:23.209
- INCLUDING MURDER.

40:23.250 --> 40:25.241
- YES, INCLUDING STABBING
AND MURDERING, I MEAN--

40:25.290 --> 40:27.019
- DOUBLE,
NOW THAT I THINK ABOUT IT.

40:27.050 --> 40:29.018
'CAUSE YOU KILLED
THAT POOR SCHLEP RUBEN LEONARD

40:29.060 --> 40:31.016
RIGHT BEFORE HE DID
THE WEATHER, ISN'T THAT RIGHT?

40:31.060 --> 40:32.152
- TWO-FOR-ONE DAY.

40:32.190 --> 40:34.158
- TWO-FOR-ONE DAY, JUDGE.

40:34.190 --> 40:35.418
- GOD.

40:35.460 --> 40:37.496
[applause]

40:37.530 --> 40:39.589
- AH, COME HERE.

40:40.970 --> 40:42.858
- WE DID IT.
YEAH.

40:44.200 --> 40:46.134
COME ON.

40:47.840 --> 40:48.636
- YEAH.

40:48.680 --> 40:53.049
[indistinct chatter]

40:58.520 --> 41:00.078
- [laughing]

41:03.690 --> 41:05.521
- H-STOCK!
- HEY, WHAT'S UP, GUYS?

41:05.560 --> 41:07.152
I JUST WANTED TO STOP BY,

41:07.190 --> 41:09.226
SAY THANK YOU AGAIN
FOR HELPING ME.

41:09.260 --> 41:10.921
AND I GOT GUS
A LITTLE SOMETHING.

41:10.960 --> 41:13.360
- OH, DUDE! MY TIE.
- CLASSY.

41:13.400 --> 41:14.890
- YEAH, GAVE ME THE CONFIDENCE
TO WIN THE CASE,

41:14.940 --> 41:16.760
BUT, UH, I DON'T NEED IT
ANYMORE.

41:16.800 --> 41:18.290
- I THINK THERE'S A STAIN
ON THIS TIE.

41:18.340 --> 41:20.968
- EH, NO STAIN.
I DON'T MEAN TO BE COCKY,

41:21.010 --> 41:22.432
BUT, UH, I FEEL LIKE
I CAN DO ANYTHING NOW.

41:22.480 --> 41:24.232
- I THINK IT'S KETCHUP.
WHO DOES THAT?

41:24.280 --> 41:26.271
WHO BORROWS A TIE
AND RETURNS IT WITH A STAIN?

41:26.310 --> 41:27.402
- HEY, SHAWN, CAN I BROACH
SOMETHING PERSONAL WITH YOU?

41:27.450 --> 41:29.475
- BROACH AWAY.

41:29.520 --> 41:31.249
- YOU KNOW THAT JUNIOR DETECTIVE
THAT YOU'RE SO SMITTEN WITH?

41:31.280 --> 41:33.043
